.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n \t\u003cli\u003eLack of domain knowledge into department-specific data sources.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n \t\u003cli\u003eComplexity associated with their growing data stack implementations.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\",\"_case_study_block_column_one_text\":\"field_6496cf1770623\",\"case_study_block_column_two_title\":\"Solution\",\"_case_study_block_column_two_title\":\"field_6496cf5170624\",\"case_study_block_column_two_text\":\"\u003cul\u003e\r\n \t\u003cli\u003eReduced implementation times with out of the box coverage for new datasets.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n \t\u003cli\u003eAutomated data lineage creation to isolate and remediate incidents.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n \t\u003cli\u003eCustom field health thresholds to meet internal SLAs.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\",\"_case_study_block_column_two_text\":\"field_6496cf6f70625\",\"case_study_block_testimonial_client_logo\":9881,\"_case_study_block_testimonial_client_logo\":\"field_6496d02a7062a\",\"case_study_block_testimonial_quote\":\"\u0022We no longer have to tailor specific tests to every particular data asset. All we really had to do was sign up, add the security implementation to give Monte Carlo the access that it needed, and we were able to start getting alerted on issues. Monte Carlo gave us that right out of the box.\u0022\",\"_case_study_block_testimonial_quote\":\"field_6496d0407062b\",\"case_study_block_testimonial_quotee\":\"Braun Reyes\",\"_case_study_block_testimonial_quotee\":\"field_6496d0747062c\",\"case_study_block_testimonial_quotee_title_position\":\"Senior Manager of Data Engineering\",\"_case_study_block_testimonial_quotee_title_position\":\"field_6496d0817062d\",\"case_study_block_testimonial_link_to_study\":{\"type\":\"post\",\"value\":\"2876\",\"title\":\"Read their story\",\"target\":false},\"_case_study_block_testimonial_link_to_study\":\"field_6496d0dc7062e\",\"case_study_block_testimonial\":\"\",\"_case_study_block_testimonial\":\"field_6496cfc370626\"},\"align\":\"\",